Package sait.frs.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidCitizenshipException
    InvalidCitizenshipException throws an exception when the user forgets to fill out the citizenship text field.
    InvalidNameException
    InvalidNameException throws an exception when the user forgets to fill out the name text field.
    NoMoreSeatsException
    NoMoreSeatsException throws an exception when there are no more seats left on the flight.
    NullFlightException
    NullFlightException throws an exception when the user forgets to enter the flight.
